get all products: http://localhost:4000/api/vi/products
post a products--admin: http://localhost:4000/api/vi/product/new
update a product--admin: http://localhost:4000/api/vi/product/<product_id>
Delete product--admin: http://localhost:4000/api/vi/product/<product_id>
Get a particular product detail:  http://localhost:4000/api/vi/product/<product_id>